{
  "stem": "17526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I can't talk about these moments because I-- I just can't finish it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "This-- these sights and these memories are with me all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And ironically, they are getting more bolder as older as I get.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I keep thinking of them more than I was thinking when I was younger-- 20 years ago, 30 years ago.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I can't talk about these things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They took me away and my sister came running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "With the truck, I remember the truck taking a sharp turn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I fell down in an open truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They took me to the-- --center where they picked up all the people that they were supposed to they had on the list to deliver.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And my sister came running with her arms stretched and this is the last I saw of my sister.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGH] And I was taken away and that's when camp life started.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I wanted to say something before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It just escaped me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It just escaped me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I-- I didn't want to get off the track, but it will probably come back to me later on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "My brother was taken after me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "There were-- later on I found out-- of course, my mother landed up in Auschwitz, I know that, and my sister landed up in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And I was told by neighbors who were on the same transport with my mother and sister-- --that survived and I met them later in Israel and they gave me an account of what they have known about my mother and sister.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "My mother was selected in Auschwitz to be in a barrack to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my sister tried to get in and they didn't let her.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
